## Society for Artificial Intelligence.

The Society for Artificial Intelligence is officially located [here](http://byui.edu/societies/society-for-artificial-intelligence). All the projects that the society's members work on is public. The repositories are located [here](https://github.com/sai-byui).
 
### Contact

For more information, please contact sofai.byui@gmail.com
